{
  "texts": [
    "Segmentation is applied to extract the region containing the lesion on an image.",
    "The next step is to extract features independently using HOG and VGG19 and make the feature vector using feature fusion.",
    "This feature vector is applied to a convolution neural network (CNN) for multiclassification.",
    "The following is a list of the utmost important contributions made by this study:",
    "• The proposed model is introduced to detect eight distinct forms of skin cancer."
  ]
}